@startuml
title MQTT publish / subscribe model

skinparam shadowing false

actor Publisher
actor Subscriber1
actor Subscriber2

component "MQTT Broker" {
}

Publisher --> "MQTT Broker" : PUBLISH topic/data
"MQTT Broker" --> Subscriber1 : data (subscribed topic)
"MQTT Broker" --> Subscriber2 : data (subscribed topic)

note right of "MQTT Broker"
Broker responsibilities:
- topic matching
- message routing
- QoS handling
end note

@enduml
